  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bavovna included! - a satirical, casual indie game - manifesto in the Shoot 'em up genre with pixel graphics about russian troops in Ukraine. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/a03200f036d229bd4250a0494e2ff29b.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/a03200f036d229bd4250a0494e2ff29b.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=49 height=72 /></picture></span>Destroy various hordes of enemies with your HIMARS in different locations and defeat their bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/eaac1f562798d531d28c59b35c09f050.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/eaac1f562798d531d28c59b35c09f050.webm?t=1774345519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/eaac1f562798d531d28c59b35c09f050.mp4?t=1774345519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not forget about upgrades, they will help you win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite