apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span><strong>Historical timeline and background of the game</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On February 24, 2022, a full-scale war began in our country - Ukraine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >russia began massive missile attacks on our cities, targeting military facilities, russian precision has already destroyed thousands of civilian homes across the country.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ukraine's partner countries, such as the USA, Germany, France, etc., predicted that Ukraine would last no more than a few days...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the time of the article, the war has been going on for over a year...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Millions of people, one way or another, faced the consequences of schizophrenia and inferiority complexes of the russian military-political leadership (aka vladimir vladimirovich putin). Tens of thousands of people have already died, including children, pregnant women, and the elderly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In the city of Mariupol alone (still occupied at the time of writing), the number of victims of russian aggression and torture is more than 20,000 people!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>(this is unofficial data, real numbers may be much higher)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The developers of the game in no way minimize the importance of war, tragedy and pain that we ourselves and our brothers and sisters have faced.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The purpose of the game is to highlight for our foreign friends the real \"greatness and might\" of the russian army.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/85848a08a602d1ae7d76dfd4897b852f.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/85848a08a602d1ae7d76dfd4897b852f.webm?t=1774345519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/85848a08a602d1ae7d76dfd4897b852f.mp4?t=1774345519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But one information field will not help our Heroes. So we decided that in addition, we will send 30% of the profit of the game to our dear volunteers: \"LNJ FUND\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, you can make a donation to the official funds for the needs of the armed forces of Ukraine by yourself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support us and together we will be able to prove that Ukrainian gamedev is really unique and advanced!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/689554456d3ec2da745ff44a40799dec.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/689554456d3ec2da745ff44a40799dec.webm?t=1774345519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/689554456d3ec2da745ff44a40799dec.mp4?t=1774345519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/a03200f036d229bd4250a0494e2ff29b.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/a03200f036d229bd4250a0494e2ff29b.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=49 height=72 /></picture></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bavovna included! - a satirical, casual indie game - manifesto in the Shoot 'em up genre with pixel graphics about russian troops in Ukraine. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/a03200f036d229bd4250a0494e2ff29b.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/a03200f036d229bd4250a0494e2ff29b.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=49 height=72 /></picture></span>Destroy various hordes of enemies with your HIMARS in different locations and defeat their bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/eaac1f562798d531d28c59b35c09f050.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/eaac1f562798d531d28c59b35c09f050.webm?t=1774345519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/eaac1f562798d531d28c59b35c09f050.mp4?t=1774345519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not forget about upgrades, they will help you win!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.apng?t=1774345519\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199830/extras/7697051b2f546d80f7d7630e66d80d7a.poster.avif?t=1774345519\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse